    <div data-cid="5655030">
        <div class="main review-item" id="5655030">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62734328/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u62734328-3.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62734328/" class="name">西北鸿烈</a>

            <span class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>

        <span content="2012-11-15" class="main-meta">2012-11-15 14:57:16</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5655030/">非现实性的斯普特尼克恋人</a></h2>

                <div id="review_5655030_short" class="review-short" data-rid="5655030">
                    <div class="short-content">

                              村上春树和昆德拉小说有一股非现实味儿，昆德拉认为小说应当挖掘生活之外的可能性，村上春树的几部作品则以现实和非现实两条线展开小说架构，在结尾将双线交合。这种非现实味儿着实诱人，摊开书，潜入小说家构造的广袤世界，一切现实中不可能的事在这里展现。           ...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5655030-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_5655030_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_5655030_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="5655030" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-5655030">
                                356
